edu.umn.biomedicus.uima.rtf

Class ControlWordCasMapping

  • edu.umn.biomedicus.uima.rtf.ControlWordCasMapping

  • public class ControlWordCasMapping

    XML bean object for a mapping from a RTF control word to a UIMA annotation. When the control word is encountered, the annotation is emitted in the output destination view.
